      <long>
	      <en>Borgbase is a simple and secure offsite backup based on the opensource Backup utility Borg.
Login into Borgbase has a couple of challenges: 
1. There is only one user.
2. User has complete access to every area
With the Borgbase GLPI integration we can:
1. Show relevant backup information: when the repo was last updated; how much space is using...
2. Get some:native Dashboard Widgets to track that information from GLPI. 
        </en>
